    {
      "id": "oB2ad20ZIJ3JxFBHqtWZM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 446.23828125,
      "y": 207.9921875,
      "width": 218.89987182617188,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bDV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1996792416,
      "version": 122,
      "versionNonce": 1975857760,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771763324795,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "req (fn & non-fn)\ncore entities\nAPI/ interfaces\nhigh level design => FN\ndeep dives => NON-FN",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "req (fn & non-fn)\ncore entities\nAPI/ interfaces\nhigh level design => FN\ndeep dives => NON-FN",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bRWQO5wqsIvDwdcsCJ5E7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 442.6099924909918,
      "y": 363.2189411879808,
      "width": 1093.5794677734375,
      "height": 1500,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bDW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 827208288,
      "version": 1855,
      "versionNonce": 484820896,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771768955588,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FUNC:\n- book tixs\n- view an event\n- search for events\n\nNON-FN:\n- consistency >> availability => strong consistency for booking tickets (no double booking)\n- availablity >> consistent for search & viewing events\n- read >> write ratio => alot more ppl viewing than buying\n- scalability to handle surges for popular events\n\nADD - low latency search\n\n-------\nOOS\n- GDPR compliance\n- fault tolerance\n\nthese are what im going to prioritize,\nis there anything that i should re-prioritize or is this okay?\n\nCore entities\n- ticket\n- buyer\n- event => out of scope to add\n- admin\n- venue\n- performer\n\ncurrently im not going to detail the key cols & fields yet, becoz the reality is that i still dk what they are yet\ntoo early in my design, & i will evolve them naturally. during the high lvl design that i would then detail them out\nfor the fields & attributes that matter\n\nAPI (strictly user interface)\n\n# view event\nGET /events/{eventId} -> Event & venue & performer & ticket [] => seat map\n\n# search event\nGET /search?term={term}&location={lat,lng}&type={type}&date={date} -> partial<Event>[]\n\n# Book ticket (2 phase)\n1. enter the booking room (reserve)\n2. is actual purchase\nPOST /booking/reserve\nheader: JWT | sessionToken\nbody: {\n    ticketId => single ticket\n}\n\nPOST /booking/confirm\nheader: JWT | sessionToken\nbody: {\n    ticketId => single ticket\n    paymentDetails (stripe) # 3rd party\n}\n\n*create API/s to satisfy reqs, and return entities/ properties/ fields\n\n* ~15 mins to get here",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FUNC:\n- book tixs\n- view an event\n- search for events\n\nNON-FN:\n- consistency >> availability => strong consistency for booking tickets (no double booking)\n- availablity >> consistent for search & viewing events\n- read >> write ratio => alot more ppl viewing than buying\n- scalability to handle surges for popular events\n\nADD - low latency search\n\n-------\nOOS\n- GDPR compliance\n- fault tolerance\n\nthese are what im going to prioritize,\nis there anything that i should re-prioritize or is this okay?\n\nCore entities\n- ticket\n- buyer\n- event => out of scope to add\n- admin\n- venue\n- performer\n\ncurrently im not going to detail the key cols & fields yet, becoz the reality is that i still dk what they are yet\ntoo early in my design, & i will evolve them naturally. during the high lvl design that i would then detail them out\nfor the fields & attributes that matter\n\nAPI (strictly user interface)\n\n# view event\nGET /events/{eventId} -> Event & venue & performer & ticket [] => seat map\n\n# search event\nGET /search?term={term}&location={lat,lng}&type={type}&date={date} -> partial<Event>[]\n\n# Book ticket (2 phase)\n1. enter the booking room (reserve)\n2. is actual purchase\nPOST /booking/reserve\nheader: JWT | sessionToken\nbody: {\n    ticketId => single ticket\n}\n\nPOST /booking/confirm\nheader: JWT | sessionToken\nbody: {\n    ticketId => single ticket\n    paymentDetails (stripe) # 3rd party\n}\n\n*create API/s to satisfy reqs, and return entities/ properties/ fields\n\n* ~15 mins to get here",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
